title: The Walking Dead Comic series issue 1 - 115 + Specials
description:
The Walking Dead Comic series issue 1 - 115 + Specials

This Month is The Walking Dead 10th Anniversary, with IMAGE releasing The Walking Dead 001 once again but this time the black and white been replaced with colour

Also this pack has been brought up to date with the missing 111 and latest issues added to the torrent and including the Tyreese Special which has also come out this week.
